HEADWORD: Phenose
<hw>Phe"nose`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Phen</ets>yl +
dextr<ets>ose</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>A sweet amorphous
